name: PrivatePageProtection
tagline: Fork of the original mediawiki extension Extension:PrivatePageProtection
body:
### Welcome to GitHub Pages.
This is a fork of the original Mediawiki extension [PrivatePageProtection](http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:PrivatePageProtection) by Daniel Kinzler ([Duesentrieb](http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/User:Duesentrieb))

####Installation
```
$ cd your_repo_root
$ git clone https://github.com/feffi/PrivatePageProtection.git
```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
